	* Addressing bug #1941962

	  The colors are still off using Pd-0.40.3-extended-20080502 on Mac
	  OS X 10.4.11 when this patch is run without adding the [pix_yuv],
	  so I added [pix_yuv] and checked the patch into CVS.	I hope it
	  works fine on Ubuntu and Windows with the [pix_yuv].

