	  verbosity

2005-07-04 13:05  zmoelnig

	* turn of debug mode

2005-07-04 11:22  zmoelnig

	* you can now specify a preferred library for decoding a file.	if
	  one is specified, it is tried as the first lib. if it fails, all
	  libs are tried in the default order (read: the specified lib is
	  tried twice: once as the preferred lib, and once as part of all
	  libs)

