2005-01-14 09:54  zmoelnig

	* added the missing " to the NEW_VIDEOFILM definition

2005-01-14 09:53  zmoelnig

	* ./configure does not call "makesource" but includes it; thus the
	  "$@" is not as expected an (empty) list of directories for which
	  we should generate Make.source but rather "dummy sh"; now we
	  check, whether the running script ($0) is "*configure", and if
	  so, we assume that the "passed" list is 0.

