	  colour-spaces b) decode YUV/Gray really fast (directly access the
	  decoding Y/U/V-planes)

2003-10-07 10:51  zmoelnig

	* added some thoughts about requested/forced colourspaces.  i
	  think, that film* should at least return colour-spaces that could
	  be handled by Gem/openGL itself.  (it doesnt make sense for
	  [pix_film] to handle IMG_FMT_RGB15) so the cs-request should
	  really be a force and not just a suggestion

