2003-07-15 09:21  zmoelnig

	* added FTGL support for text-rendering under macOS i have made
	  FTGL the default (not knowing whether it will break) under windos
	  GLTT is still the default (although FTGL should work too) under
	  linux the configure script decides what to take, but prefers FTGL
	  rather than GLTT

